breakingChangesNotes:
• The deprecated command `wab-get-metadata-of-one-or-multiple-sessions` has been removed.
  • The deprecated argument `application_put__meters` has been removed from the `wab-edit-application` command.
  • The deprecated output `WAB.profile_get.gui_features.dashboards` has been removed from the `wab-get-profile` and `wab-get-profiles` command.
  • The deprecated output `WAB.application_get.tags.id` has been removed from the following commands: `wab-get-application`, `wab-get-applications`.
  • The deprecated output `WAB.device_get.tags.id` has been removed from the following commands: `wab-get-device`, `wab-get-devices`.
